        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 6. Reinhardorhynchus ruffinjonesi (Karling, 1978) comb. n.. A–F, hard structures of the copulatory bulb. A–B, from the holotype. C–D, specimen from Cuba. E, specimen from Punta Culebra (Panama). F, specimen from Brazil. E oriented with proximal end toward top of figure; the others with proximal end toward left of figure." ;
